title.narrative: Migration Communication Campaigns in Nigeria and Iraqi Kurdistan

description.narrative: A strategic communications campaign to help potential migrants in Nigeria and Iraqi Kurdistan to better understand the risks, realities, and facts of irregular migration. This will enable them to make a more informed decision about irregular migration to Europe. An LGBTQ component is being piloted in KRI and an educational outreach component in Nigeria.
